A N D _ M U C H _ M O R E !

MAP BRIEFING

The terrorists have targetted a famous resort in Finland and have decided to make their action as the sun starts to set and place starts to close. While terrorists were waiting in their vans, local over heard the terrorists plan and reports this to the police and as the terrorists start to move, they're waiting, but the terrorists aren't unarmed.

OBJECTIVE
Terrorists: Plant the bomb on "sauna", area (A) on the map (Screenshot E) and Demolish the nice vacation resort along with its residents.
Counter terrorists: Protect the sauna from demolition by all cost!

MAP INFORMATION

Map contains: "UFO, NPC, finnish flag, statues, secret areas etc.."
Recommented players/Max players: 20/64
Map contains a single bomb site.
Spawnpoints: Terrorists spawn from the garage near vans, from there they have 3 main ways to the bomb zone. Counter terrorists spawn from lobby close to the bomb zone.
All of the map, isn't in the screenshots, EXPLORE!

Download --> Test --> Comment --> Rate.

Kittehs will thank you!
